Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:37.38,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}探して見つけ出すために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:42.52,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}遅く起きた朝でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:49.18,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}毎日目を覚ますんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:51.78,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:55.35,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:23:01.68,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ちょっとでも笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:07.87,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}いつだってこの世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:14.53,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたが必要だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:16.71,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:19.62,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:23.70,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:30.79,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:37.38,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}究竟为了追寻什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:42.52,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}睡过头的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:49.18,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}也日复一日地清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:23:01.68,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:07.87,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}因为这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:14.53,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}总是需要你的存在
